    <item>
      <title>由于通胀风险持续存在，印度央行维持关键利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/india-central-bank-holds-key-rate-as-inflation-risks-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行连续第七次在政策会议上维持基准利率不变，因为对即将到来的热浪的警告再次引发了人们对通胀飙升的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/india-central-bank-holds-key-rate-as-inflation-risks-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 04:35:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
